'''High Lord''' (feminine '''High Lady''') was the title of the head of one of the [[Tapani Noble Houses|noble houses]] of the [[Tapani sector/Legends|Tapani sector]]. Originally, the heads of the Houses were [[King/Legends|kings]] of feuding states, until [[Shey Tapani]], High Lord of [[House Melantha]], became [[Emperor (Tapani)|Emperor]] of the [[Tapani]] sector, and the kings became High Lords.

==Notable High Lords / Ladies==
*[[Emperor (Tapani)|Emperor]] [[Shey Tapani]] - [[House Melantha]]
*Lord [[Tritum XI]] - [[House Mecetti]]
*Lady [[Brezwalt III]] - House Mecetti
*Lady [[Varin Arabella]] - [[House Barnaba]]
*Lady [[Bathos]] - [[House Cadriaan]]
*Lord [[Weston Warsheld]] - [[House Calipsa]]
*Lord [[Bodé Leobund XI]] - House Mecetti
*Lord [[Bal Jaset]] - [[House Melantha]]
*Lord [[Theus Paddox]] - [[House Pelagia]]
*Lord [[Galen Panos]] - [[House Reena/Legends|House Reena]]

